title: William Johnstone -Eagles 05 Rage of Eagles
description: An adventure, a love story, an epic of courage, loyalty, honor, and betrayal, this fifth book in the acclaimed "Eagles" series plunges MacCallister into the harshness of the awakening West. Spanning a decade, sweeping from New Mexico Territory and the Lincoln County War to an untamed settlement called Tombstone, Falcon's daring quest will make him not only an eyewitness to history, but a catalyst in the most enduring of our national myths.
